edu.usc.scrc.PriorityPruner
Class CommandLineOptions

java.lang.Object
  edu.usc.scrc.PriorityPruner.CommandLineOptions

public class CommandLineOptions
extends java.lang.Object

This class defines and parses the command line options given as input to the program. It uses the Apache Commons CLI 1.2 library for both specifying and parsing the options.
